OL,6,FThe Court of Appeal part allowed an
OL,7,Fappeal taken by several Troubles
OL,8,Fvictims against the body created by
OL,9,Fthe last government's contentious
OL,10,FLegacy Act.
OL,12,FJudgment was delivered at the Royal
OL,13,FCourts of Justice on Friday by
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland's Lady Chief Justice
OL,15,FDame Siobhan Keegan sitting with
OL,16,Ffellow appeal court judges Lord
OL,17,FJustice Horner and Mr Justice
OL,18,FScoffield.
