OL,4,Cdisclosure ruled unlawful
OL,6,FThe appeal was mounted after a High
OL,7,FCourt judge ruled in February that the
OL,8,Flegislation underpinning the
OL,9,Fcommission did not contravene human
OL,10,Frights laws and the body could
OL,11,Fundertake effective investigations of
OL,12,FTroubles murders.
OL,14,FThe Court of Appeal judges dismissed
OL,15,Fsome grounds of the appeal, such as
OL,16,Fthe fact the commission is bound by a
OL,17,Ffive-year time limit on accepting
OL,18,Finvestigation requests.
