OL,7,FGovernment appeal in relation to the
OL,8,FWindsor Framework and upheld the
OL,9,Foriginal High Court judgment.
OL,11,FThe ICRIR was set up in May under the
OL,12,FLegacy Act.
OL,14,FMany families who lost loved ones
OL,15,Fduring the conflict claim the
OL,16,Fcommission lacks the teeth and
OL,17,Findependence to properly re-examine
OL,18,Ftheir cases.
