OL,6,FOne of the most controversial
OL,7,Fprovisions of the Act was the offer of
OL,8,Fa form of conditional immunity to
OL,9,Fperpetrators of Troubles crimes who
OL,10,Fagreed to co-operate with the new
OL,11,Ftruth recovery commission.
OL,13,FThe Labour Government has already
OL,14,Fcommitted to repeal the immunity
OL,15,Fprovision and also the Act's ban on
OL,16,Fcivil cases and inquests related to
OL,17,FTroubles incidents.
