OL,6,FIt has however pledged to retain the
OL,7,FICRIR. In justifying the retention of
OL,8,Fthe commission, the Government had
OL,9,Fcited February's High Court judgment
OL,10,Fby Mr Justice Colton.
OL,12,FThe Court of Appeal judgment, which
OL,13,Fhas found the ICRIR to be incompatible
OL,14,Fwith the ECHR on the key issue of
OL,15,Fdisclosure, will undoubtedly intensify
OL,16,Fcalls from some victims'
OL,17,Frepresentatives for the commission to
OL,18,Fbe scrapped.
