OL,7,FNorthern Ireland's former lord chief
OL,8,Fjustice Sir Declan Morgan.
OL,10,FOutside court one of the bereaved
OL,11,Frelatives who mounted the appeal
OL,12,Fcalled on him to quit.
OL,14,FMartina Dillon, whose husband Seamus
OL,15,Fwas shot dead by loyalists in
OL,16,FDungannon in 1997, told reporters:
OL,17,F"Today was a brilliant day for
OL,18,Fvictims. We've won. We've won what we
OL,19,Fwanted."
